Transient Utility AddApp
------------------------

*AddApp <directory>.<wildcard>

Will scan <directory> for things matching <wildcard> and will an entry into
Resources:$.Apps for each thing matching <wildcard>. This command assumes
the things are applications, and will create a directory with 1, 2 or 3 of
!Boot, !Help and !Run in it as appropriate.

Example:
AddApp SCSI::HardDisc4.$.Apps.!*
will add all applications inside $.Apps.
